<sample sampleID="LBk9_00129" version="1.0" type="fixedLength">
<article articleID="LBk9_00129_F001">
<quotation>
<speech>
<paragraph>
<sentence>それに対<sampling type="start" />して<quote>「ぶらつく」</quote>は場所が決まっていないと。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">―</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ただ、<quote>「うろつく」</quote>には不審・不快なイメージが含まれることが多い。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">椎</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　じゃあ、おれたちのがだいたい当たっているな。</sentence>
<sentence>特に沢野の答えが正解なような気がする<noteMarker text="＊１２" />。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<noteBody>
<sentence>１２　友人にさりげなく花を持たせようとする発言、との解釈もあるが、本当に沢野が正解したという驚き、との解釈もある。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</noteBody>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">―</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence><quote>「解説」</quote>と<quote>「説明」</quote>に行きましょうか。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">椎</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　アイロンが<quote>「説明」</quote>で、ワープロが<quote>「解説」</quote>。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">木</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　アイロン？</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">椎</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　アイロンの<quote>「説明書」</quote>だよ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">目</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ようするに、簡単なやつが<quote>「説明」</quote>で、難しいものが<quote>「解説」</quote>だって言いたいんでしょ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">椎</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　そう。</sentence>
<sentence><quote>「説明」</quote>が入門篇で、<quote>「解説」</quote>が専門篇。</sentence>
<sentence>ようするに、<quote>「解説」</quote>のほうがランクが上なんだよ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">目</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ま、それに近いんだけど、<quote>「説明」</quote>は表面上のことを説明するだけで<quote>「解説」</quote>はその仕組みから解きあかすこと。</sentence>
<sentence>つまり、もっと内部に入り込んでいくのね。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">木</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　おれの解釈はこうだね。</sentence>
<sentence>野球の場合、ルールの説明と解説は違うだろ。</sentence>
<sentence>その違いだよ<noteMarker text="＊１３" />。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<noteBody>
<sentence>１３　本人は違うと思っているようだが、直前の目黒の解釈と同じである。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</noteBody>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">沢</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　アイロンとワープロでいいんじゃない。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">椎</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　麻雀で徹夜したときが<quote>「説明」</quote>で、浮気で徹夜したときが<quote>「解説」</quote>（笑）。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">木</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　たしかに<quote>「説明しなさい」</quote>と言われても<quote>「解説しなさい」</quote>とは言われないな（笑）。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">目</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　だから何なんだよ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">椎</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　解答に行こうぜ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">―</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　<quote>「解説」</quote>は、ものごとを分析して他人によくわかるように述べること。</sentence>
<sentence><quote>「説明」</quote>は、ものごとの根拠が明らかになるように述べること。</sentence>
<sentence>どう違うんでしょうか。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">木</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　根拠ねえ。</sentence>
<sentence><quote><sentence>「なぜ遅くなったの？</sentence>
」</quote>とか<quote>「<sentence>なぜワイシャツに口紅がついてるの？</sentence>
」</quote>とか<quote>「<sentence>なんで妙な香水の匂いがするの？</sentence>
」</quote>ということに対して、根拠を説明するのか？</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">―</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　わかった。</sentence>
<sentence>浮気したことを説明するのが本人で、解説するのが他人。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">木</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　<quote>「あそこの夫婦はこういうわけで喧嘩になった」</quote>と言うのが<quote>「解説」</quote>か（笑）。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">椎</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　で、正解者がいたのか？</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">目</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　いない。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">木</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　いいところまでは行ったんだけどな。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">間違えやすい言葉Ⅱ</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">椎</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　間違えやすい言葉の続きをやろうぜ。</sentence>
<sentence>問題を読むのは浜本な。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">―</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　はい。</sentence>
<sentence>じゃあ、<quote>「回転」</quote>と<quote>「転回」</quote>から行きます。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">椎</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　いきなり難しいな。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">沢</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　いや、簡単だよ。</sentence>
<sentence>回転寿司ってあるだろ。</sentence>
<sentence>あれは、全体がまわっているでしょ。</sentence>
<sentence>そういうのが回転。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">目</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　じゃあ、転回は何なんだよ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">沢</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　寿司そのものがくるくるまわっちゃう（笑）。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">椎</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　それだな（笑）。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">目</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　本当かよ。</sentence>
<sentence>違うと思うなあ。</sentence>
<sentence><quote>「回転」</quote>はモノなんじゃないかなあ。</sentence>
<sentence><quote>「転回」</quote>はモノとはかぎらない。</sentence>
<sentence>たとえば、歴史が転回するって言うじゃない。</sentence>
<sentence>歴史は回転しないよ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">椎</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　その説もいいかもしれない。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">木</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ストーリー展開と言うなあ。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">目</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　その<quote>「展開」</quote>は違うでしょ。</sentence>
<sentence>ここは<quote>「転回」</quote>。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">椎</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　おれ、ひらめいた。</sentence>
<sentence>右まわりが<quote>「回転」</quote>で、左まわりが<quote>「転回」</quote>（笑）。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">―</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　ええと、解答に行きます。</sentence>
<sentence><quote>「回転」</quote>はコマのように定位置でぐるぐるまわること。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">目</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　おー。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
<quotation>
<speech>
<speaker>
<sentence type="quasi">椎</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</speaker>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　これ<sampling type="end" />は沢野説じゃないか。</sentence>
</paragraph>
</speech>
</quotation>
</article>
</sample>
